msg: Fixed callback style asynchronous invocations (made sure that callback is executed only once) and some thread issues in AsyncCallbackFuture.java (multiple clients concurrently waiting for the returned Future to be 'done').
Made the bus's automatic workqueue the default executor associated with a Service (different to server side, where the executor associated with an Endpoint is null by default).
